  <bodyText><![CDATA[<!-- REMOVE THIS OFFER ON MONDAY 28TH DECEMBER -->
<p><a name="#6"></a></p>
<p><strong>Day 6: Advent Window – Sunday 6th December – <em>WIN TWO FREE LIFT PASSES FOR CHAMPOLUC</em></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Valid on the first new booking made to the Chalet Hotel Champoluc departing 16th January 2016.</li>
<li>Bookings must be for 7 nights or longer booked by midnight on Wednesday 23rd December.</li>
<li>To enter please call our Reservations team on 01483 345 718 or ask your Travel Agent to call on your behalf.</li>
<li>Our Reservations team will be keeping track for the first booking made for this departure date before Wednesday 23rd December.</li>
<li>Inghams will notify the winner when the first booking has been made.</li>
<li>Prize is not transferrable and no cash alternative can be offered.</li>
<li>If the holiday is cancelled the prize will be null and void.</li>
</ul>
<!-- REMOVE THIS OFFER ON TUESDAY 29TH DECEMBER -->
<p><a name="#19"></a></p>
<p><strong>Day 19: Advent Window – Saturday 19th December – <em>WIN A FREE NIGHT AT THE BLOC HOTEL GATWICK AIRPORT</em></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Valid on the first three new bookings made on one of our Northern Norway Winter breaks tours travelling in February or March 2016.</li>
<li>Bookings must be made by midnight on Sunday 27th December.</li>
<li>Stays at the BLOC Hotel London Gatwick must be taken before 30th April 2016.</li>
<li>To enter please call our Reservations team on 01483 345 718 or ask your Travel Agent to call on your behalf.</li>
<li>Our Reservations team will be keeping track for the first 3 bookings made for this departure date before 27th December and notify the winners as the successful bookings are made.</li>
<li>Winner will be sent a voucher from Inghams for the BLOC hotel for you to book your required night directly with them, subject to availability.</li>
<li>Prize is not transferrable and no cash alternative can be offered.</li>
</ul>
<!-- REMOVE THIS OFFER ON MONDAY 28TH DECEMBER -->
<p><a name="#23"></a></p>
<p><strong>Day 23: Advent Window – Wednesday 23rd December – <em>WIN A PAIR OF MENS HIKING BOOTS</em></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>To enter please <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.facebook.com/inghams/" target="_blank">visit our <strong>Facebook page</strong></a> and follow our instructions for our Advent mens hiking boots post before midnight on Wednesday 23rd December.</li>
<li>Winners will be selected on Thursday 24th December and will be contacted by Inghams.</li>
<li>Hiking boots are a mens size 8, 9 or 10.</li>
<li>Open to UK residents only.</li>
<li>The prize will be dispatched in early January.</li>
<li>Prize is not transferrable and no cash alternative can be offered.</li>
</ul>
<!-- REMOVE THIS OFFER ON WEDNESDAY 30TH DECEMBER -->
<p><a name="#24"></a></p>
<p><strong>Day 24: Advent Window – Thursday 24th December – <em>WIN ONE OF FOUR SKI GOODY BAGS</em></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>To enter please <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.facebook.com/inghams/" target="_blank">visit our <strong>Facebook page</strong></a> and follow our instructions for our Advent ski goody bag post before midnight on Monday 28th December.</li>
<li>Winners will be selected on Tuesday 29th December and will be contacted by Inghams.</li>
<li>Open to UK residents only.</li>
<li>The prize will be dispatched in early January.</li>
<li>Prize is not transferrable and no cash alternative can be offered.</li>
</ul>]]></bodyText>
